translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「さぁ、どうだどうだ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "So, how about it? How about it?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「手応えよかったぞ、どうだ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "That felt good, didn't it? How is it!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ごほっ、おごっ、ぅ、ぐ……ぜぇ、はぁ……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Cough, cough, ugh, gu... huff, ha..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: な、なに、を……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "W-What... are you..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「うがーーーーーーーー！！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Ughhhhhhhhhhhh!!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「はい生存！　セーーーッフ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Alive! Safe!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 蹴りつけた魔物兵は天を仰いで悔しがり、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The monster soldier he kicked looked up to the sky in frustration,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 見ていた魔物兵は拳を突き上げて喜んだ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The watching monster soldiers raised their fists in joy.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「手加減キック3連勝だな、はっはっは。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Three consecutive wins with those mild kicks, haha."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: アウトならガキとかジジババ狙うのがコツだぜ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "The trick is to target kids or old folks if they're out."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「くっそ、イケると思ったのに……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Damn, I thought I had him..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 生きてんじゃねーよ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Don't still be alive!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ひぐぶっ……！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Higub...!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: もう一撃、蹴りを見舞われて、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: He was hit with another kick,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 通行人は動かなくなった。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: And the passerby stopped moving.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「よっしゃ、じゃあいくか。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Alright then, let's go."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 目を付けてたトコがあんだよ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "I have a place I've been aiming for."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔物兵は、ひょいと果物屋の軒先に入った。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The monster soldier casually entered the fruit seller's porch.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ひっ、魔物……！？　あ……や、いやっ……！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Eek, a monster...!? Ah... no, no...!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: やだ、やめてっ……いやああぁぁっ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Stop, no... please stop... nooooo!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「へへへへへ！　叫べ叫べ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Hehehehe! Scream, scream!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「おっほ、いい泣き声……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Oh ho, that’s a nice crying voice..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: おーい、順番後でいいから俺も俺もー」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Hey, order can wait, I want in too, me too!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 屋敷の二階から、都市長は一部始終を眺めていた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: From the second floor of the mansion, the city governor watched everything unfold.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: （これで正しい……正しいのだ……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: (This is right... It is right...)

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 必要な犠牲、なのだ……耐えてくれ……）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The necessary sacrifice... Please endure it...)

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: マルリラの周辺の都市では、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: In the cities around Marurira,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: お互いに団結し、戦い続けようという動きもあった。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: There were movements to unite and continue fighting together.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: だがそれらは陥落後に奪い尽くされ焼き尽くされ、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: But those were all plundered and burned after falling,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 更地になった所さえある。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: There were even places reduced to barren land.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そうした街に比べれば、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Compared to such towns,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 現状でもまだマシなはずだった。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Things were still better as they were now.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「うぇーす」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Yo."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「うっ……また来たのか」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Ugh... They came again?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「こっちもね、仕事なんでね。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Well, this is our job too."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: お宅様の金銀はね、没収だね」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Your gold and silver will be confiscated."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ま、まってくれ！　もう、街の金はない！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "W-Wait! The town's money is all gone!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 本当だ！　残りは、私個人のささやかな……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "It's true! What remains is only my own modest..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ああ。だからそれを徴集に来たんだって」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Yeah. That's exactly why we came to collect it."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「なッ……わ、私の身と財産は、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Wha... My person and property were supposed to be..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 保証してくれるはずでは……！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...guaranteed!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「しらねーよ。こっちは大将軍閣下の命で
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "I don't care. We're just following the orders of the Great General."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: やってるだけなの。おい、やるぞー」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That's all we're doing. Hey, let's do this."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ういーす」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Yes, sir."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔物兵たちは部屋の中を荒らし始めた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The monster soldiers began ransacking the room.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 机を叩き割って中を探り、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They smashed the desk and searched inside,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 衣装箪笥から取りだした服の飾りをむしり取る。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: And ripped decorations off clothes taken from the wardrobe.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「よ、よせ、やめてくれ……！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "S-Stop it, please...!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 大将軍を呼んでくれ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Call the Great General!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「おう、もう始めているのか」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Oh, you've already started."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ぴ、ピサロ大将軍……！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "G-Great General Pisaro...!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 何故こんな無体をするのだ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Why are you committing such atrocities!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「外じゃ面白半分で死んでる奴も多いのに、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Many outside die just for fun though,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 大げさな奴だな」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You're being exaggerated."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「それは、っ……いや、その……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "That is... well, um..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: し、しかし、約束が違う！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: But, the promise is different!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「全ての金銀は俺の物だ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "All the gold and silver belong to me.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 貴様に認めた財産というのは、それ以外だ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: What I recognized as your property is other than that."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「そ……それ、以外……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Th-That, other than that..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: マルリラの周辺の都市では、

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: There were movements to unite and continue fighting together.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: だがそれらは陥落後に奪い尽くされ焼き尽くされ、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: But those were all plundered and burned after falling,

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: There were even places reduced to barren land.

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Compared to such towns,

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "I don't care. We're just following the orders of the Great General."

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Many outside die just for fun though,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「それは、っ……いや、その……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "That is... well, um..."
